In the midst of the Democratic-led House Judiciary Committee’s new investigation into President Donald Trump, House Minority Whip Steve Scalise (R-La.)
is calling out Democrats’ “end game” — to impeach Trump.
GOP Scalise swiped back at House Democrats seeking to dig up information on Trump.
“They don’t want to get the facts,” Scalise said on Fox News.
"They don't want to get the facts," Scalise said.